skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: space astronauts
des: Gives a list of astronauts that are currently working in space from all over the world. An API is used here to get the data (http://api.open-notify.org/astros.json), there are no such hardware prerequisites required, you just need an Alexa and Amazon account and you are good to go!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
